snippet.title: Super Donkey Kong 64 Release Trailer
snippet.description:
For more fangames, subscribe to this channel!
https://www.youtube.com/c/KazeEmanuar?sub_confirmation=1

Mario and Pauline decide to give their friend, DK, a visit to talk about old rivalries. But when they arrive, all Kongs seem missing.
This mod has 50 stars.
You can download it here:
https://mega.nz/#!KGpwTQIS!obsCOS6qpJh7C-J6xpSXQkMw-ePdl3ZkX5EfN_JmSRQ

How to play in Project64 1.6:
1. open rom
2. options-settings-unmark "hide advanced settings"
3. close options
4. options-settings-rom settings
5. set RDRAM to 8MB and counter factor to 1

Credit to:
Skill (model ripping tools, https://banjosbackpack.com/forums/forum.php )
UED (ripping the levels, ideas, https://www.youtube.com/user/UED)
DobieMeltfire (music conversions, https://www.youtube.com/user/DobieMeltfire)
Greenthunder (music conversions, https://www.youtube.com/c/mrgreenthunderx)
